About this item

  • Dimension of keyboard wrist rest: 17.72 x 3.15 inch, that of mousepad wrist support: 9.84 x 7.87 inch. Fits all mouse/keyboard. Compatible with MacBook / Notebook / Chromebook / Ultrabook / Desktop / PC, also compatible with iMac.
  • Ergonomically designed with breathable/durable neoprene cloth and raised memory foam. Efficient for easy typing & pain relief. Offers soft support to relieve pressure and pain of your wrist, keep your wrist in a natural and comfortable state.
  • Non-slip base can firmly grasp the desk to prevent sliding or any unintentional movement.
  • Edges is reinforced to endure long-time use. The filled cushion part will slowly rebound when leave it, not easy to deform.
  • Perfect for OL gamer and programmer used in home / office. Suitable for friend, family member and yourself.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
